<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8" standalone="yes"?>
<bug>
	<id>14797</id>
	<title>User Text should be required when reporting  Other  Facebook policy violation</title>
	<description>
		<paragraph id="1">
			<sentence id="1.1">A few times a year I receive an email from Facebook informing me that a user reported my application as violating Facebook policy.</sentence>
			<sentence id="1.2">The emails always state that the user selected  Other  as the violation category.</sentence>
			<sentence id="1.3">These emails include additional text provided by the user_ which is invariably blank.</sentence>
			<sentence id="1.4">How helpful!</sentence>
			<sentence id="1.5">(not)</sentence>
		</paragraph>
		<paragraph id="2">
			<sentence id="2.1">I propose that Facebook should make the additional text provided by the user as required when reporting a violation of category  Other .</sentence>
		</paragraph>
		<paragraph id="3">
			<sentence id="3.1">Following is an example of the emails I receive:</sentence>
		</paragraph>
		<paragraph id="4">
			<sentence id="4.1">Dear App Developer_</sentence>
		</paragraph>
		<paragraph id="5">
			<sentence id="5.1">A Facebook user requested that we forward an anonymous report that your app BirthWatch (app ID #xxxx) is violating Facebook Policy.</sentence>
			<sentence id="5.2">The user selected  Other  as the violation category.</sentence>
			<sentence id="5.3">Any additional text that the user provided appears here:</sentence>
		</paragraph>
		<paragraph id="6">
			<sentence id="6.1">[[ Begin User Text ]]</sentence>
		</paragraph>
		<paragraph id="7">
			<sentence id="7.1">[[ End User Text ]]</sentence>
		</paragraph>
		<paragraph id="8">
			<sentence id="8.1">To protect the privacy of our users_ we cannot disclose any further information.</sentence>
			<sentence id="8.2">Facebook is not taking any action against your app based on this particular report_ but we are passing this along so you are made aware of potential problems and respond accordingly to ensure you are in compliance.</sentence>
			<sentence id="8.3">Please note that failure to comply with Facebook policy may result in an enforcement action.</sentence>
		</paragraph>
		<paragraph id="9">
			<sentence id="9.1">If you have any issues or questions_ please don t hesitate to contact us directly by using the Developer Contact Form at: http://www.facebook.com/developers/developer_help.php</sentence>
		</paragraph>
		<paragraph id="10">
			<sentence id="10.1">Thanks_</sentence>
		</paragraph>
		<paragraph id="11">
			<sentence id="11.1">Facebook</sentence>
		</paragraph>
	</description>
</bug>
